outputs.output_descr: Increase the capacity of stakeholders in the electoral process to ensure improved public participation and confidence in the democratic transition process. This includes technical assistance and providing international experience and best practices to national authorities responsible for the electoral process, notably to the election management body, strengthening the capacity of civil society organizations to play its roles in the electoral process effectively, produce public outreach tools and strengthen the capacity of women in politics to take part in the electoral process as candidates. This is an electoral cycle project designed to cover the first and second-generation elections.
